'''瑞安·詹姆斯·肖克洛斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Ryan James Shawcross'''}}，{{bd|1987年|10月4日|catIdx=Shawcross, Ryan}}）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，出身[[曼聯預備隊及青訓學院|曼聯青訓系統]]，司職[[後衛_(足球)#中后卫|中堅]]，現效力於[[美職|美職]]球會[[迈阿密国际足球俱乐部|國際邁阿密]]。

==生平==
===早年===
梳爾哥斯在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[柴郡|柴郡]]接近[[威爾士|威爾士]]邊界的[[郡治|郡治]][[切斯特|切斯特]]出生，父母均為威爾士裔。少年時曾代表夫林特夏男童隊（Flintshire Boys）比賽，而[[加里·斯皮德|史必]]、[[迈克尔·欧文|奧雲]]及[[伊恩·拉什|魯殊]]等亦曾在此踢球<small><ref name="Ryan Shawcross Bio">{{cite web |url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/players/profile?id=89557&cc=4716 |title=Ryan Shawcross Bio |work=[[ESPN|ESPN]]soccernet |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2010-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305073933/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/players/profile?id=89557&cc=4716 |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

===球會===
梳爾哥斯出身[[曼聯|曼聯]]青訓系統，在2005/06年球季獲提升加入預備隊，是這支初級三冠球隊的主力成員之一。2006年10月25日首次代表一隊在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第三圈作客[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克魯]]於[[加時賽|加時]]後補上陣，最終以2-1獲勝晉級。

2007年1月梳爾哥斯被外借到[[比利时足球乙级联赛|比利时乙级联赛]]的[[皇家安特卫普足球俱乐部|皇家安特卫普]]協助爭取升級，梳爾哥斯成為球隊的常規正選，效力直到球隊於附加賽敗陣錯失升級機會才返回曼聯，期間上陣22場及射入3球。

2007年8月9日梳爾哥斯再次被外借，今次留在本土加盟[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]6個月<small><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stokecityfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10310~1088202,00.html |title=Shawcross Signs! |date=2007-08-09 |accessdate=2009-02-09 |work=史篤城官網 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6939666.stm |title=Stoke City sign Shawcross on loan |date=2007-08-09 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016231301/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/6939666.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，他在為球隊上陣首兩場比賽各射入一球，首球在聯賽揭幕戰作客[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]一箭定江山，協助球隊旗開得勝<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/6931081.stm |title=Cardiff 0-1 Stoke |date=2007-08-11 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport }}{{en}}</ref></small>；另一球於[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|罗奇代尔]]在開賽後僅4分鐘先開紀錄，但最終到[[加時賽|加時]]仍踢成2-2平手，[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]更以2-4落敗<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/6941887.stm |title=Rochdale 2-2 Stoke City (aet) |date=2007-08-14 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport }}{{en}}</ref></small>。梳爾哥斯繼續有優異的表現，在10月時更分別在對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]、[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:科尔切斯特;zh-hk:高車士打}-]]及[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]取得入球，使他成為該月份「英冠每月最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7080062.stm |title=Shawcross receives October award |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602184904/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7080062.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。 

史篤城原本希望續借梳爾哥斯到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7132698.stm |title=Shawcross wants to stay at Stoke |date=2007-12-07 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217225505/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7132698.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，但急不及待在2008年1月轉會窗重開時將梳爾哥斯正式收歸旗下<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7176695.stm |title=Shawcross set for permanent move |date=2008-01-08 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2008-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112114333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7176695.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，交易於1月18日落實，初步轉會費為100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，將來按出場次數及史篤城的成績計算而可能加倍金額，簽約三年半<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Shawcross ties up £1m Stoke move |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7176695.stm |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-18 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2008-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112114333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7176695.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。4月27日梳爾哥斯入選[[PFA年度最佳陣容|2008年PFA年度英冠最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |title=Ronaldo named player of the year |date=2008-04-27 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616234859/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，4月28日梳爾哥斯獲選為史篤城年度最佳青年球員<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7373255.stm |title=I owe a lot to Pulis - Shawcross |date=2008-05-01 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217225214/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7373255.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，5月4日史篤城於主場0-0賽和[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]後，確保聯賽亞席及自動升級[[英超|英超]]<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7368631.stm |title=Stoke 0-0 Leicester |date=2008-05-04 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107214800/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7368631.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2008年8月16日史篤城作客[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，是梳爾哥斯及球隊在英超的處女賽，但表現糟透了，以1-3敗陣而回<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Bolton 3-1 Stoke |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7551165.stm |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-16 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122150231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7551165.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。賽後備受抨擊未達英超水平的梳爾哥斯被領隊[[東尼·佩利斯|東尼·佩利斯]]（Tony Pulis）貶到後備席<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Shawcross out to silence critics |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7864305.stm |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-04 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028151505/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7864305.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，由新簽入的[[阿卜杜拉耶·迪亚涅-法耶|戴安尼菲爾]]取代其中堅位置，令到梳爾哥斯一度考慮離隊<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Shawcross may look to leave Stoke |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7584752.stm |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-28 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-date=2019-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415152613/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7584752.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。梳爾哥斯一直等到10月19日主場對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]才再有機會後補上場<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7665101.stm |title=Stoke 2-1 Tottenham |date=2008-10-19 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122124810/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7665101.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，10月26日作客[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]重返正選陣容，但卻讓[[罗比尼奥|羅賓奴]]撕破防線而大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，以0-3大敗一場<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7674116.stm |title=Man City 3-0 Stoke |date=2008-10-26 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113024834/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7674116.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。11月1日主場2-1擊敗[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，梳爾哥斯接應[[羅里·德拉普|戴納]]的「手榴彈」在敵方門前製造混亂，間接助攻入第二球<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7684755.stm |title=Stoke 2-1 Arsenal |date=2008-11-01 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2017-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209073210/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7684755.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，而其過份「硬朗」的踢法亦令[[雲加|雲加]]在賽後略有微言<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7708886.stm |title=Wenger furious at Stoke tackling |date=2008-11-05 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031172012/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7708886.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>，但梳爾哥斯辯稱他無意傷害其他球員，只是公平競賽<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7710894.stm |title=Stoke boss fears referee backlash |date=2008-11-06 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201064005/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7710894.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。11月15日首次重返[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]對[[曼聯|曼聯]]，卻以0-5慘敗而回<small><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711301.stm |title=Man Utd 5-0 Stoke |date=2008-11-15 |accessdate=2009-02-05 |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2009-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113011937/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711301.stm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。2009年3月1日作客[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，在落後0-2下梳爾哥斯推上前助攻，在88分鐘接應[[比亞堤|比亞堤]]傳球頂入個人[[英超|英超]]的首個入球，最後史篤城更於完場前扳平取得寶貴的1分<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7905869.stm |title=Aston Villa 2-2 Stoke |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-01 |accessdate=2009-03-23 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121100108/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7905869.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。一不離二，3月21日主場對護級對手[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]，於84分鐘接應[[羅里·德拉普|戴納]]的「手榴彈」在離門6[[碼|碼]]頂入致勝一球，1-0戰果同時將史篤城帶離降級區域<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7937095.stm |title=Stoke 1-0 Middlesbrough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-21 |accessdate=2009-03-23 |archive-date=2020-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212231848/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7937095.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2010年2月28日在主场再次对阵阿仙奴，梳爾哥斯一个铲截导致对方中场球员[[阿隆·拉姆塞|拉姆塞]]断腳<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8530490.stm |title=Stoke 1-3 Arsenal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-27 |accessdate=2010-03-01 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309132145/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8530490.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但当天梳爾哥斯即被[[卡佩罗|卡佩罗]]召入[[英格兰足球代表队|国家队]]。

2013年1月3日史篤城宣佈與梳爾哥斯簽五年半新合約，令其留隊至2018年夏季<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Skipper signs long-term contract at the Club |url=http://www.stokecityfc.com/news/article/shawcross-agrees-deal-576655.aspx |publisher=stokecityfc.com |date=2013-01-03 |accessdate=2013-01-03 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111215715/https://www.stokecityfc.com/news/article/shawcross-agrees-deal-576655.aspx |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
2008年1月梳爾哥斯首次獲徵召加入[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-21]]出戰[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]預選賽對愛爾蘭U-21<small><ref>{{cite news |title=Shawcross gets international call |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/stoke_city/7220423.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2008-02-05 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。在此之前他曾經代表威爾斯U-15對賽[[比利時|比利時]]及[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]<small><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fawtrust.org.uk/files/WSFA%20U.16%20&%20U.15%20Squads.doc |title=National Development Squad (Year 86) |work=[[威爾斯足球總會|威爾斯足球總會]] |accessdate=2009-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305213245/http://www.fawtrust.org.uk/files/WSFA%20U.16%20%26%20U.15%20Squads.doc |archive-date=2016-03-05 |dead-url=yes }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2010年2月28日，梳爾哥斯首次獲徵召加入[[英格兰足球代表队|英格兰足球代表队]]出战对阵[[埃及国家足球队|埃及]]的世界杯[[热身赛|热身赛]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8541108.stm |title=Ryan Shawcross named in England squad for Egypt match |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-27 |accessdate=2010-03-01 |archive-date=2020-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200129062029/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8541108.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

